Same Adishakti enlightens individually all the three forms of God

00:01:57.363 --> 00:01:59.710
which you know

00:02:00.028 --> 00:02:04.351
whose name is Bramha, Vishnu and Mahesh means is Shiv Shankar.

00:02:05.149 --> 00:02:08.355
That means three aspects of one diomand

