and when on Doomsday, the whole creation

00:02:25.424 --> 00:02:31.880
the whole manifested world is immersed

00:02:31.905 --> 00:02:34.903
merges with the same Bramha

00:02:35.928 --> 00:02:40.931
even then Sadashiva is present there

00:02:42.045 --> 00:02:44.790
and His connection

00:02:46.691 --> 00:02:51.137
continues with that part of God

00:02:51.162 --> 00:02:53.791
which is never manifested

00:02:54.530 --> 00:02:57.882
which is a non- being.

00:02:57.907 --> 00:03:08.168
God's powers that manifest, come out of His Being

00:03:08.732 --> 00:03:12.783
and those which do not manifest, always remain as non being.

00:03:13.085 --> 00:03:16.926
In that Sadashiva's place

00:03:18.426 --> 00:03:25.133
is like a diamond which may break, get splitted

00:03:25.158 --> 00:03:30.054
however much it may get smashed , break into small particles

00:03:30.546 --> 00:03:33.612
still it goes on shining.

00:03:34.954 --> 00:03:40.088
It's shine never gets destroyed.

00:03:40.113 --> 00:03:44.322
This is what Sada Shiv’s state is.

00:03:46.124 --> 00:03:51.093
A state (STHITI) is created because of Sada Shiva

00:03:51.118 --> 00:03:55.589
and in the creation of the world

00:03:56.883 --> 00:04:02.418
unless there is a situation there can be no creation.

00:04:03.113 --> 00:04:06.198
First of all, a situation is created.

00:04:06.223 --> 00:04:09.857
Existence of anything is to be brought about.

00:04:10.362 --> 00:04:17.560
Existence is caused because of the power of Sadashiva.

00:04:20.431 --> 00:04:29.992
That is why, His role in creation is the same

00:04:30.017 --> 00:04:38.953
as that of foundation of a massive building.

00:04:38.986 --> 00:04:46.144
Foundation cannot be seen

00:04:46.169 --> 00:04:51.499
but without that no building can be erected.

00:04:52.462 --> 00:04:56.058
In the same way, Sadashiva inside our being

00:04:56.083 --> 00:05:00.228
resides in our heart and takes the form of spirit.

00:05:00.514 --> 00:05:04.572
Till He is in  the form of spirit in our heart

00:05:04.775 --> 00:05:10.623
till then only our life in this world continues.

00:05:10.648 --> 00:05:15.976
The day He closes His eyes, the same day we cease to exist.

00:05:16.651 --> 00:05:23.487
We leave this world and our state goes to PARLOK (another world).

00:05:24.780 --> 00:05:34.654
Shivji, you know resides in our Moon Channel.

00:05:35.703 --> 00:05:40.529
and residing in our Moon channel

00:05:40.554 --> 00:05:45.379
He does His work of maintaing its STHITI (state) within us.

00:05:45.922 --> 00:05:56.020
But He also maintains the state of our PRANA (life).

00:05:57.716 --> 00:06:01.333
Without Shivji our life cannot continue.

00:06:01.358 --> 00:06:04.371
There is a detailed description of it

00:06:04.396 --> 00:06:06.997
which I have mentioned in detail in My book.

