Shivji's form is that He is a great Saint.

00:06:16.155 --> 00:06:20.452
For example, God's form is that He is a saint from within

00:06:24.880 --> 00:06:27.513
He doesn't have any reason to do it He does it.

00:06:27.577 --> 00:06:30.581
He does it because of His whim, for His joy.

00:06:30.606 --> 00:06:33.742
If He wants, He creates, otherwise He destroys.

