and whatever we enjoy in the world

00:07:39.144 --> 00:07:43.092
that enjoyment form of the God Almightly

00:07:43.117 --> 00:07:46.175
is that of Shree Vishnu's form.

00:07:47.093 --> 00:07:49.739
