You already know that He drank all the poison in the beginning only

00:09:10.295 --> 00:09:13.650
and whatever poison of the world is there

00:09:13.675 --> 00:09:17.196
He consumes inside His being and keeps the world cool

00:09:18.323 --> 00:09:20.787
to give joy to the creation.

