Whatever dies or comes to an end

00:09:25.647 --> 00:09:31.358
goes and settles down in His kingdom

00:09:31.579 --> 00:09:35.257
and all the useless and the evil people's

00:09:35.669 --> 00:09:40.609
prisons are shut down by the dust of His feet.

00:09:41.564 --> 00:09:47.477
They are controlled by the grateness of Shivji.

00:09:50.115 --> 00:09:53.693
Chandrama (Moon) resides on His head.

